<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-575] Partition.makeFollower() reads broker info from ZK</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-575</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;To follow a new leader, Partition.makeFollower() has to obtain the broker info of the new leader. Currently, it reads that info from ZK for every affected partition. This increases the time for a leader to truly available. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
